# DevMetrics page.tsx Refactoring Guide

This file documents exactly what needs to be extracted from the monolithic `page.tsx` (959 lines) into a clean component architecture.

## Target File Structure

```
src/
  constants/
    themes.ts          # THEMES array + Theme type
    urls.ts            # PROD_DOMAIN + URL builder helpers
    navigation.ts      # Nav links, step data, feature data
  types/
    cards.ts           # CardResultProps, SnippetRowProps, etc.
  hooks/
    useClipboard.ts    # clipboard copy + copied state
    useMounted.ts      # delayed mount flag for hydration
    useCardGenerator.ts # username, theme, options state + URL builders
  components/
    icons/
      GithubIcon.tsx
      CopyIcon.tsx
      CheckIcon.tsx
      ChevronUpIcon.tsx
      ChartIcon.tsx
      CodeIcon.tsx
      PinIcon.tsx
    ui/
      CopyButton.tsx       # Reusable copy-with-feedback button
      CodeBlock.tsx         # Styled <pre> block for markdown snippets
      ThemeSelect.tsx       # Theme dropdown
      LayoutSelect.tsx      # Layout dropdown
      ToggleCheckbox.tsx    # Labeled checkbox toggle
    cards/
      CardResult.tsx        # Stats/langs preview card
      RepoPinCard.tsx       # Repo pin card with instructions
      SideBySideCard.tsx    # Side-by-side layout card
    layout/
      Header.tsx
      Footer.tsx
      HeroSection.tsx
      ResultsSection.tsx
      CustomizeBar.tsx
    sections/
      HowItWorks.tsx       # StepBox grid
      Features.tsx          # FeatureBox grid
      ThemeGallery.tsx      # Theme grid with previews
      Documentation.tsx     # DocSection + DocParam + QuickStartBlock
    StickyBar.tsx            # Bottom sticky copy bar
  app/
    page.tsx               # Thin orchestrator (~50-80 lines max)
```

## Extraction Priority

1. **Constants** → `src/constants/` (quick win, zero risk)
2. **Types** → `src/types/cards.ts` (enables better DX)
3. **Hooks** → `src/hooks/` (useClipboard, useMounted, useCardGenerator)
4. **Icons** → `src/components/icons/` (7 inline SVGs to extract)
5. **UI primitives** → `src/components/ui/` (CopyButton used 5+ times)
6. **Section components** → `src/components/sections/`
7. **Layout** → `src/components/layout/`

## Key Patterns to Eliminate

### Repeated Copy Button (5+ instances)
Extract into `<CopyButton copied={copied === id} onClick={() => onCopy(text, id)} />`.

### Repeated Code Block (4+ instances)
Extract into `<CodeBlock>{content}</CodeBlock>` with consistent styling.

### URL Building Logic
Move `buildParams()` and all URL derivations into `useCardGenerator` hook or a pure utility.

### Inline SVG Paths
The `FeatureBox` component has an `iconMap` record — replace with proper icon components.
